 []}, {'message_id': '19dbd11974908f86', 'thread_id': '19dbd11974908f86', 'from': 'Kujou2 <cm.carla03@gmail.com>', 'subject': 'Escalation: Repeated Failed Delivery | Order #44022-FD', 'date': 'Fri, 24 Apr 2026 09:18:47 +0800', 'internal_date': '1776993527000', 'label_ids': ['CATEGORY_PERSONAL', 'INBOX'], 'body': '*Dear Logistics Manager,*\n\nI am escalating a recurring delivery failure for the following order which\nhas now exceeded our standard three-attempt protocol.\n\n -\n\n *Order Number:* #44022-FD\n -\n\n *Customer Name:* Elena Rodriguez\n -\n\n *Issue:* Incorrect Address / Access Code Required\n -\n\n *Incident Summary:* The driver has attempted delivery three times since\n Tuesday. The customer claims the address provided is correct but notes that\n the gate code provided in the delivery notes is being ignored by the\n courier.\n\nCan we coordinate a specific delivery window or verify if the driver has\nthe updated access instructions?', 'has_attachments': False, 'attachments': [], 'body_full': '*Dear Logistics Manager,*\r\n\r\nI am escalating a recurring delivery failure for the following order which\r\nhas now exceeded our standard three-attempt protocol.\r\n\r\n   -\r\n\r\n   *Order Number:* #44022-FD\r\n   -\r\n\r\n   *Customer Name:* Elena Rodriguez\r\n   -\r\n\r\n   *Issue:* Incorrect Address / Access Code Required\r\n   -\r\n\r\n   *Incident Summary:* The driver has attempted delivery three times since\r\n   Tuesday. The customer claims the address provided is correct but notes that\r\n   the gate code provided in the delivery notes is being ignored by the\r\n   courier.\r\n\r\nCan we coordinate a specific delivery window or verify if the driver has\r\nthe updated access instructions?\r\n', 'body_links': []}, {'message_id': '19dbd1134a9fe302', 'thread_id': '19dbd1134a9fe302', 'from': 'Kujou2 <cm.carla03@gmail.com>', 'subject': 'URGENT: Escalation - Lost Parcel | Order #88291-LP', 'date': 'Fri, 24 Apr 2026 09:18:22 +0800', 'internal_date': '1776993502