 regards,\\n\\nCharles Michael Carla', 'has_attachments': False, 'attachments': [], 'body_full': 'Dear Customer Service Team,\\r\\n\\r\\nI am writing to express my dissatisfaction with the delivery process for my\\r\\nrecent order, 88292.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe package failed to arrive within the timeframe promised at checkout, and\\r\\nI received no proactive communication regarding this delay. Reliable\\r\\ndelivery is a critical part of the shopping experience, and unfortunately,\\r\\nthis order fell well short of expectations.\\r\\n\\r\\nI would appreciate it if you could investigate why this delay occurred and\\r\\nprovide me with an update on when I can expect consistent service in the\\r\\nfuture.\\r\\n\\r\\nBest regards,\\r\\n\\r\\nCharles Michael Carla\\r\\n', 'body_links': []}, {'message_id': '19dc60f52e5a0dd3', 'thread_id': '19dc60f52e5a0dd3', 'from': 'Carlos Miguel Carla <cm.carla03@gmail.com>', 'subject': 'Commendation for Great Service \u2013 [#88291]', 'date': 'Sun, 26 Apr 2026 03:12:53 +0800', 'internal_date': '1777144373000', 'label_ids': ['UNREAD', 'IMPORTANT', 'CATEGORY_PERSONAL', 'INBOX'], 'body': 'Dear Customer Service,\\n\\nI am writing to express my sincere appreciation for the assistance I\\nreceived regarding my order 88291.\\n\\nI had a specific inquiry, and your representative handled it with\\nremarkable professionalism and efficiency. It is rare to receive such\\nhigh-quality support, and I wanted to ensure this positive experience was\\nrecognized.\\n\\nThank you for your excellent service. It is a pleasure dealing with a team\\nthat clearly values its customers.\\n\\nBest regards,\\n\\nCharles Michael Carla', 'has_attachments': False, 'attachments': [], 'body_full': 'Dear Customer Service,\\r\\n\\r\\nI am writing to express my sincere appreciation for the assistance I\\r\\nreceived regarding my order 88291.\\r\\n\\r\\nI had a specific inquiry, and your representative handled it with\\r\\nremarkable professionalism and efficiency. It is rare to receive such\\r\\nhigh-quality support, and I wanted to ensure this positive experience was\\r\\nrecognized.\\r\\n\\r\\nThank you for your excellent service. It is a pleasure dealing with a team\\r\\nthat clearly values its customers.\\r\\n\\r\\nBest regards,\\r\\n\\r\\nCharles Michael Carla\\r\\n', 'body_links': []}, {'message_id': '19dc5eabe3a1bba9', 'thread_id': '19dc5ea75fbc9049', 'from': 'carlosmiguel.carla.cics@ust.edu.ph', 'subject': '', 'date': 'Sat, 25 Apr 2026 11:33:09 -0700', 'internal_date': '1777141989000', 'label_ids': ['SENT'], 'body': 'FOR REVIEW: Issue: Missing shipment for Order #88291-LP. Timeline: Parcel marked as delivered at 10:15 AM on April 24, 2026, but CCTV shows no carrier arrival. Severity: High, potential misdelivery or theft. Last known location was the North Distribution Hub.\\n\\nDear Kujou2,\\n\\nWe sincerely apologize for the inconvenience caused by the missing shipment for Order #88291-LP. We understand the urgency of this matter and are currently investigating the GPS coordinates of the delivery scan. Our team is working diligently to resolve this issue and will provide you with an update by the end of the day. In the meantime, please let us know if there is any additional information you can provide that might assist in our investigation.\\n\\nThank you for your patience and understanding.\\n\\nBest regards,\\n[Your Name]\\nLogistics Manager\\n\\n--- \\nThis is written by Assistant Agent', 'has_attachments': False, 'attachments': [], 'body_full': 'FOR REVIEW: Issue: Missing shipment for Order #88291-LP. Timeline: Parcel marked as delivered at 10:15 AM on April 24, 2026, but CCTV shows no carrier arrival. Severity: High, potential misdelivery or theft. Last known location was the North Distribution Hub.\\n\\nDear Kujou2,\\n\\nWe sincerely apologize for the inconvenience caused by the missing shipment for Order #88291-LP. We understand the urgency of this matter and are currently investigating the GPS coordinates of the delivery scan. Our team is working diligently to resolve this issue and will provide you with an update by the end of the day. In the meantime, please let us know if there is any additional information you can provide that might assist in our investigation.\\n\\nThank you for your patience and understanding.\\n\\nBest regards,\\n[Your Name]\\nLogistics Manager\\n\\n--- \\nThis is written by Assistant Agent', 'body_links': []}, {'message_id': '19dbd121c7e38917', 'thread_id': '19dbd121c7e38917', 'from': 'Kujou2 <cm.carla03@gmail.com>', 'subject': 'COMPLAINT: Professional Conduct/Handling | Order #11055-C', 'date': 'Fri, 24 Apr 2026 09:19:21 +0800', 'internal_date': '1776993561000', 'label_ids': ['CATEGORY_PERSONAL', 'INBOX'], 'body': '*Dear Logistics Manager,*\\n\\nA formal complaint has been lodged regarding the handling of a recent\\ndelivery.\\n\\n -\\n\\n *Order Number:* #11055-C\\n -\\n\\n *Customer Name:* Marcus Thorne\\n -\\n\\n *Type of Complaint:* Damaged Property / Driver Conduct\\n -\\n\\n *Incident Summary:* The customer reported that the courier threw the\\n package over a 6-foot fence, resulting in the destruction of the fragile\\n contents. The customer has provided photos of the damaged goods and the\\n placement of the parcel.\\n\\nThis requires immediate attention to resolve the customer\u2019s dissatisfaction\\nand to address the handling procedures with the specific carrier involved.', 'has_attachments': False, 'attachments': [], 'body_full': '*Dear Logistics Manager,*\\r\\n\\r\\nA formal complaint has been lodged regarding the handling of a recent\\r\\ndelivery.\\r\\n\\r\\n   -\\r\\n\\r\\n   *Order Number:* #11055-C\\r\\n   -\\r\\n\\r\\n   *Customer Name:* Marcus Thorne\\r\\n   -\\r\\n\\r\\n   *Type of Complaint:* Damaged Property / Driver Conduct\\r\\n   -\\r\\n\\r\\n   *Incident Summary:* The customer reported that the courier threw the\\r\\n   package over a 6-foot fence, resulting in the destruction of the fragile\\r\\n   contents. The customer has prov