[2026-04-26 04:48:40.271] [PRINT]       "body": "Dear Management Team,\n\nI am writing to formally complain about the conduct of the delivery driver\nwho handled my order, 88294, on April 25, 2026.\n\nDuring the delivery, the driver was unprofessional and dismissive when I\nattempted to interact with them. This behavior does not align with the\nprofessional standards I expect from your company.\n\nI believe it is important for you to be aware of this incident to ensure\nbetter service standards for your customers moving forward. I would\nappreciate confirmation that this feedback has been noted.\n\nBest regards,\n\nCharles Michael Carla",
[2026-04-26 04:48:40.271] [PRINT]       "has_attachments": false,
[2026-04-26 04:48:40.271] [PRINT]       "attachments": [],
[2026-04-26 04:48:40.271] [PRINT]       "body_full": "Dear Management Team,\r\n\r\nI am writing to formally complain about the conduct of the delivery driver\r\nwho handled my order, 88294, on April 25, 2026.\r\n\r\nDuring the delivery, the driver was unprofessional and dismissive when I\r\nattempted to interact with them. This behavior does not align with the\r\nprofessional standards I expect from your company.\r\n\r\nI believe it is important for you to be aware of this incident to ensure\r\nbetter service standards for your customers moving forward. I would\r\nappreciate confirmation that this feedback has been noted.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\n\r\nCharles Michael Carla\r\n",
