[2026-04-26 04:48:40.271] [PRINT]       "body_full": "*Dear Logistics Manager,*\r\n\r\nWe have received an urgent report regarding a missing shipment. Despite the\r\n\"Delivered\" status in the system, the customer has confirmed they have not\r\nreceived the item.\r\n\r\n   -\r\n\r\n   *Order Number:* #88291-LP\r\n   -\r\n\r\n   *Customer Name:* Jordan Smith\r\n   -\r\n\r\n   *Last Known Location:* North Distribution Hub\r\n   -\r\n\r\n   *Incident Summary:* Parcel was marked as delivered at 10:15 AM today,\r\n   but CCTV footage from the residence shows no carrier arrival. Initial\r\n   tracing suggests a potential misdelivery or theft.\r\n\r\nPlease investigate the GPS coordinates of the delivery scan and advise on\r\nthe next steps for a replacement or claim.\r\n",
[2026-04-26 04:48:40.271] [PRINT]       "body_links": []
