[2026-04-26 04:48:40.271] [PRINT]             "body": "FOR REVIEW: Issue: Missing shipment for Order #88291-LP. Timeline: Parcel marked as delivered at 10:15 AM on April 24, 2026, but CCTV shows no carrier arrival. Severity: High, potential misdelivery or theft. Last known location was the North Distribution Hub.\n\nDear Kujou2,\n\nWe sincerely apologize for the inconvenience caused by the missing shipment for Order #88291-LP. We understand the urgency of this matter and are currently investigating the GPS coordinates of the delivery scan. Our team is working diligently to resolve this issue and will provide you with an update by the end of the day. In the meantime, please let us know if there is any additional information you can provide that might assist in our investigation.\n\nThank you for your patience and understanding.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]\nLogistics Manager\n\n--- \nThis is written by Assistant Agent",
